content:
This clone trooper served on Kamino under Jedi Master Shaak Ti during the Clone Wars. In 20 BBY, this trooper was tasked with tracking down Advanced Recon Clone CT-5555, nicknamed "Fives", who had gone rogue shortly after learning of Inhibitor chips placed within the minds of all clone troopers.
This Clone trooper was equipped with Phase II clone trooper armor adorned with dark gray markings, a kama and a visor with an Aurebesh "C" painted on the sides.
The clone trooper captain debuted, albeit unnamed, in the third episode of the sixth season of the animated series Star Wars: The Clone Wars. The episode aired on February 15, 2014, and was voiced by Dee Bradley Baker like all clones in The Clone Wars. The clone trooper is identified as a captain in the script.
